    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and there isn't a single mark on it. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Come take a look and see for yourself, you won't be disappointed! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
