    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS for instantaneous throttle response. This example is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the rod bearing service has been proactively performed, and the rear subframe has been fully reinforced to eliminate common structural fatigue. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping and rebound characteristics, with no signs of bushing deflection. This is a turn-key, concours-level specimen with zero deferred maintenance and a pristine chassis.",
